-- Buffett-Backed Automaker BYD First-Quarter Profit Surges 255% on Sales
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-26T13:17:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/buffett-backed-automaker-byd-first-quarter-profit-surges-255-on-sales.html

          
          
             BYD Co., the Chinese automaker
backed by Warren Buffett, said first-quarter net income rose 255
percent to 1.7 billion yuan.  
 Sales rose 70 percent to 12.7 billion yuan, the company
said in a statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange today.
Earnings per share rose 226 percent to 0.75 yuan, the company
said.  
          
          


  


        